import React from 'react'
import { Icon } from 'semantic-ui-react';

const CornerIcon = () => (
    <React.Fragment>
      <Icon.Group size='big'>
        <Icon name='mail outline' />
        <Icon corner='top right' name="user" as="div"/>
      </Icon.Group>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
  
  export default CornerIcon
